quran[7]{c,v,t}:
  1,1,"In the name of Allah, the Entirely Merciful, the Especially Merciful"
  1,2,"Praise be to God, Lord of the Universe"
  1,3,"The Merciful, the Compassionate"
  1,4,Sovereign of the Day of Judgement
  1,5,"You alone we worship, and to You alone we turn for help"
  1,6,Guide us to the straight path
  1,7,"The path of those whom You have favoured, Not of those who have incurred Your ire, Nor of those who have lost their way"
